nodes.bodyText: Since it appears in a couple places for this method, may be useful to have a named constant in this method for the value 5, similar to what was done in testStreamTaskLogWithNegative().
Similar to what was previously done in extensions-core/google-extensions/pom.xml, does it make sense to have the 1.26.0 suffix value provided by the com.google.apis.client.version property?
